{% comment %}
  About / Our Story — Field section (text + bullet list on the left, founders
  photo with sun sticker on the right). Self-contained literal copy + assets.
{% endcomment %}

<section class="about-field about-field-{{ section.id }} color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">
  <div class="about-field__container">

    <div class="about-field__text-col">
      <div class="about-field__body">
        <p>Years later, that same instinct pulled us back into the field in 2025. We travelled across the country armed with notebooks, questions, and a very stubborn <strong>belief</strong> that <strong>Indian ingredients deserved more respect than they were getting.</strong></p>
        <p>We met farmers who treated their crops not as commodities but as an extension of their own identity. We also saw the parts no one talks about: sacks stored in damp godowns, produce mixed across grades, and adulterants added to pure ingredients.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-field__list-wrapper">
        <p>Slowly, a clear picture emerged:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>farmers were growing high-quality produce</li>
          <li>trader and wholesaler mismanagement was letting contamination enter the supply chain</li>
          <li>consumers who wanted to eat better couldn&rsquo;t do so</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-field__image-col">
      <div class="about-field__image-wrapper">
        <img
          src="{{ 'about-founders.jpg' | asset_url }}"
          alt="The founders in the field, somewhere in the Western Ghats"
          width="800"
          height="548"
          loading="lazy"
          class="about-field__main-img"
        >

        <div class="about-field__sticker" aria-hidden="true">
          <img src="{{ 'about-sun.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="120" height="117" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="about-field__caption">(somewhere in the Western Ghats)</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
  .about-field {
    background-color: #fbf3cc;
    padding: 10px 20px;
  }

  .about-field__container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 60px;
    padding-top: 30px;
  }

  .about-field__text-col {
    flex: 1;
    color: #5d57c5;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family, "Aesthet Nova", Georgia, serif);
  }

  .about-field__body {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .about-field__body p {
    margin: 0 0 1em;
  }

  .about-field__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-field__body strong {
    color: #5d57c5;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .about-field__list-wrapper p {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0 0 0.4em;
  }

  .about-field__list-wrapper ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 10px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-field__list-wrapper li {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
    color: #5d57c5;
  }

  .about-field__list-wrapper li::before {
    content: "\2022";
    color: #5d57c5;
    font-weight: bold;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .about-field__image-col {
    flex: 0 0 45%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-field__image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .about-field__main-img {
    width: 80%;
    margin-top: -80px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: block;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
  }

  .about-field__sticker {
    position: absolute;
    top: -118px;
    right: 64px;
    width: 80px;
    height: auto;
    z-index: 2;
    transform: rotate(15deg);
  }

  .about-field__sticker img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-field__caption {
    margin-top: 15px;
    margin-right: 85px;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family, "Aesthet Nova", Georgia, serif);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #5d57c5;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-field__container {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .about-field__image-col {
      width: 100%;
      flex: auto;
    }

    .about-field__sticker {
      width: 60px;
      top: -20px;
      right: -10px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-field {
      padding: 20px 12px;
    }

    .about-field__container {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    .about-field__image-col {
      width: 100%;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-field__image-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-evenly;
    }

    .about-field__main-img {
      width: 90%;
      margin-top: 0;
      box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.08);
    }

    .about-field__sticker {
      width: 48px;
      top: -10px;
      right: 10px;
      transform: rotate(10deg);
    }

    .about-field__caption {
      margin-right: 0;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-field__text-col {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-field__body {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .about-field__list-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .about-field__list-wrapper ul {
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .about-field__list-wrapper li {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      padding-left: 16px;
    }

    .about-field__list-wrapper p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Story Field",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Color scheme",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "About Story Field" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
